title: Earth warrior
pluck off
description: I've noticed the featherpluckers seem to be out in full force again. For those of you not familiar, a featherplucker is someone who intentionally votes 1 heart on a palette just to lower its score. Why do they do it you might ask? I'm thinking the answer lies somewhere in the colour names... I'm not saying everyone has to like all the palettes all the time, but it is rather suspicious when you start to see the scores of once high-ranking palettes fall off suddenly. It doesn't take a math wizard to figure out it's the work of a featherplucker. It's sad really...but as you can see...very inspiring. :D
